PEAK,helps,users,create,and,stick,to,training,plans,for,cycling,running,swimming,triathlons,MTB,and,cross,country,skiing,The,service,responds,dynamically,to,changes,in,the,users,plans,and,helps,calculate,an,appropriate,training,load,PEAK,also,includes,a,nutrition,app,that,specifies,what,and,how,much,the,user,should,be,eating,based,on,their,activities,The,PEAK,API,enables,developers,to,access,the,entirety,of,PEAK,s,Dynamic,Training,Platform,from,their,applications